      • getMonitorClasses

        public java.util.List<GsonMonitorClasses.MonitorClasses> getMonitorClasses()
        Gets the list of cached monitor classes. If a list exists, called monitorclasses, it is returned. If a list does not exist but a single monitor class exists, a list of one element is returned. If nothing is set, returns null.
        Returns:
